Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.56,0:41:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rjómo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.88,0:41:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rjómo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.54,0:41:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Musím jít.
